若[[函数|实函数]]$$f(x)$$在点$$x_0$$的[[邻域]]$$U(x_0)$$内有定义，且在$$x_0$$处[[可导]]

$$
\forall x\in U(x_0), f(x)\le f(x_0) \implies f'(x_0)=0
$$

对偶地，

$$
\forall x\in U(x_0), f(x)\ge f(x_0) \implies f'(x_0)=0
$$
